data.title: 145 ORGSbyCompanyName
data.meta_description: 145-ORGSbyCompanyName - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document is a list of 253 approved European 145 organizations by company name. It provides the company name, approval number, address, phone and fax numbers for each approved maintenance organization. The organizations are located across Europe and have approval from various national aviation authorities and EASA.
